    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BREAKER: INITIATING</strong>是一款简短的3D横向卷轴游戏，以解谜与平台跳跃元素为游戏核心。你将化身成机器人El，逃离神秘的巨大设施，在文明的断垣残壁中探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个恶劣的后末日世界，人类进入了冰封设施进行休眠，被遗留的机器在没有人类的世界渐渐演化出新的机械生态。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原被封存在研究机构中的机械人El，因意外解封逃出后，一步一步向外探索环境......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012360/extras/df34d067d25a22803da7803ccfa9aaed.poster.avif?t=1727755256\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012360/extras/df34d067d25a22803da7803ccfa9aaed.webm?t=1727755256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012360/extras/df34d067d25a22803da7803ccfa9aaed.mp4?t=1727755256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
